title: Your Destiny Supersedes Your Mistakes | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Your Destiny Supersedes Your Mistakes | Joel Osteen
description:
When we make a mistake, it’s easy to feel like we’ve missed God’s plan for our lives. But nothing you’ve done is a surprise to God. He’s already prepared a comeback for that setback.


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
